title: The Pregnant Virgin | Ep. 2
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: There's a day when (almost) every woman loses her v-card, and it's something you never forget, whether it was awful, awesome or somewhere in between. In today's episode you'll hear more than you probably want to about our experiences.
